chart.name: Memory Paging
chart.programText:
A = data('swap.in', filter=filter('plugin', 'swap') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).publish(label='A')
B = data('swap.out', filter=filter('plugin', 'swap') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).publish(label='B')

chart.name: CPU %
chart.programText:
A = data('cpu.utilization', filter=filter('plugin', 'signalfx-metadata') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).mean(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Total Network Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('net.err_in', filter=filter('agent', 'telegraf') and filter('plugin', 'net') and filter('interface', 'e*')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('net.err_out', filter=filter('agent', 'telegraf') and filter('plugin', 'net') and filter('interface', 'e*')).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A + B).sum().publish(label='C')

chart.name: Disk Used %
chart.programText:
A = data('disk.utilization', filter=filter('plugin', 'signalfx-metadata') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).mean(by=['plugin_instance']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('diskio.reads', filter=filter('agent', 'telegraf') and filter('plugin', 'diskio')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('diskio.writes', filter=filter('agent', 'telegraf') and filter('plugin', 'diskio')).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: # Active Hosts
chart.programText: A = data('mem.free', filter=filter('plugin', 'mem') and filter('agent', 'telegraf'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).count().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Total Disk I/O Ops
chart.programText:
A = data('diskio.writes', filter=filter('plugin', 'diskio') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('diskio.reads', filter=filter('plugin', 'diskio') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Memory Used %
chart.programText:
A = data('memory.utilization', filter=filter('plugin', 'signalfx-metadata') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Network Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('net.err_in', filter=filter('plugin', 'net') and filter('interface', 'e*') and filter('agent', 'telegraf'), rollup='delta').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('net.err_out', filter=filter('plugin', 'net') and filter('interface', 'e*') and filter('agent', 'telegraf'), rollup='delta').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A + B).sum().publish(label='C')

chart.name: Disk Free %
chart.programText:
A = data('disk.utilization', filter=filter('plugin', 'signalfx-metadata') and filter('agent', 'telegraf')).mean(by=['plugin_instance']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (100 - A).publish(label='B')

chart.name: Top 5-min Load Avg

chart.name: Total Disk Space
